</P>
<P>
REI, an outdoor gear and clothing firm, will present a lecture on gray whales 
at 6:30 p.m. Thursday at 3029 University Ave., San Diego. Admission free. For 
more information, call (619) 295-7700. 
</P>
<P>
 -- -- -- 
</P>
<P>
Previews of discount cruises and rail tours will be discussed by Los Coyotes 
Travel at 7:30 p.m. on Jan. 25 at the Sequoia Club, Beach Boulevard at 
Orangethorpe, in Buena Park. Admission free, but reservations required. For 
more information and tickets, call (714) 670-1184 or toll-free (800) 346-4317. 
</P>
<P>
