Orange County Community College District at 7 p.m. on Jan. 25 in the Board 
Room, District Education Center, 1000 N. Lemon St., Fullerton. Admission free. 
For more information, call (714) 871-4030, extension 15. 
</P>
<P>
 -- -- -- 
</P>
<P>
The first of a three-part lecture and slide show on Australia will be held by 
One for the Road Travel Club Jan. 27 at 7:30 p.m. at Glendale Federal Savings, 
722 E. Colorado Blvd., Pasadena. Admission is a $5 donation. For more 
information and reservations, call (818) 569-0235. NORMAN DASH 
