<P>
Series 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA011589-0077 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 5641 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
January 15, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
