profit although operating at far less than capacity. ; Photo, JoAnn Gertsman, 
left, and Betty Wilburn own Justina's, a restaurant that opened a year and a 
half ago on Pine Avenue in Long Beach and has undergone bankruptcy 
reorganization. AXEL KOESTER / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Al Williams ; Map, 
