<HEADLINE>
<P>
SHOPPING CART PERIL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
It is getting to be impossible to walk or to ride in most cities of Orange 
County without bumping into shopping carts. They are everywhere. They are very 
dangerous to pedestrians and drivers. 
</P>
<P>
Let that be our New Year's resolution: Don't leave carts everywhere. 
</P>
<P>
HERMAN and MINNIE SCHECHTER 
</P>
<P>
Fullerton 
</P>
