</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
COACHES; LOS ANGELES DODGERS (BASEBALL TEAM); BASEBALL WRITERS ASSOCIATION OF 
AMERICA; HONORS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA011589-0191 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 5923 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
January 15, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part 3; Page 2; Column 2; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
26 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE: NAMES IN THE NEWS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
