MONDAY CLOSINGS: MARTIN LUTHER KING JR. DAY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MAIL: There will be no delivery Monday, with post offices closed. 
</P>
<P>
SCHOOLS: Public schools will be closed Monday. 
</P>
<P>
BANKS: Most banks and savings &amp; loans will be closed. 
</P>
<P>
GOVERNMENT: Monday is a holiday for federal, state and county government 
offices. City offices in Huntington Beach, Irvine and Santa Ana will be closed; 
all others will be open. 
</P>
<P>
REFUSE: There will be no residential trash pickup in Santa Ana on Monday; 
regular pickup schedules for the week will move back one day. Schedules in all 
other cities will be unchanged. 
</P>
